Module FlightBookingSystem_Dist

Package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.gui

package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.gui
This package contains the graphical user interface (GUI) classes for the flight booking system. It includes classes for the main window, booking window, and other UI components that interact with the user and display information.
Since:
2024-06-24
Version:
1.0
